{"tid":1533940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅與北韓外長會面談及香港局勢","createTime":"2019-09-03T00:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:55:41.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e78df0170026216fc89afd5941c7112810eedf","tid":1533940,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/王毅與北韓外長會面談及香港局勢-002034465.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E8%88%87%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2%E8%AB%87%E5%8F%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-002034465.html&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a70a9a6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/王毅與北韓外長會面談及香港局勢-002034465.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】正在北韓訪問的國務委員兼外長王毅，跟北韓外長李容浩會面，談及香港局勢。<br />\n<br />\n二人在平壤萬壽台議事堂舉行會談。王毅介紹當前香港局勢，以及中方立場舉措。李勇浩則指北韓已多次表明在香港問題上的立場，並願意再次重申香港是中國的香港，外部勢力不應干涉，北韓黨和政府堅決支持中國黨和政府維護「一國兩制」，捍衛國家主權和領土完整。<br />\n<br />\n雙方又就朝鮮半島局勢深入交換意見，同意繼續保持密切溝通，為維護地區和平穩定作出更大貢獻。"},{"pid":"1b8fdebfb1eed796d8c26a3c0f3e9c88b3e45d88","tid":1533940,"uid":209614,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:56:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d3601508d31a9fda04e4da26801f3ec9c4c0560","tid":1533940,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:57:12.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史